title: Week’s Best Dressed: 7 Outfits You Need to See
text: Yahoo Style November 18, 2016 It has been a crazy week filled with events! So many stars, so many gorgeous looks. It was tough to narrow it down to just seven women. At Glamour’s Women of the Year Awards, Jenna Dewan Tatum had a Cleopatra vibe with her bright green turtleneck dress. As for Gigi Hadid, she once again looked effortlessly chic in her silk pajama ensemble. Amy Adams was a standout in her red Tom Ford cutout gown at the premiere of T om Ford’s “Nocturnal Animals.” To see even more best-dressed looks of the week, watch the video above.
